<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/744212-shouldn-t-these-books-be-read-in-order-if">Shouldn&#39;t these books be read in order if they are a serial?
l</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_744212'><a id="like_count_community_question_744212" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/744212?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">2 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F820480.Revelation">like</a></span>

